            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Apollini et <lb n="2"/>Dianae <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umerus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Brit</abbr><ex>tonum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>et <expan><abbr>explorat</abbr><ex>ores</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Nemaning</abbr><ex>enses</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uram</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>agen</abbr><ex>te</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aurel</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Firmino |(centurione) <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXII <expan><abbr>Pr</abbr><ex>imigeniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aeti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> Idibus <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>Augus</abbr><ex>tis</ex></expan> Orfito <lb n="10"/>et Rufo co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar, Sockel und Bekrönung abgeschlagen. B: Mattern: Z. 6: c(enturio). Auf der linken Nebenseite dreibeiniger Klapptisch, mit Becher und Brot(?) gedeckt. Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
            </div>
